label.phrase: if any person shall write print utter or publish any false scandalous and malicious 376 u s 254 274 writing or writings against the government of the united states or either house of the congress or the president with intent to defame or to bring them or either of them into contempt or disrepute or to excite against them or either or any of them the hatred of the good people of the united states
